# Build intermediates: objects, PRGs, test transcripts. One tree per
# toolchain -- the two share no object code. The finished archives land in
# dist_ca65/ and dist_llvm/, which are committed for users who only want
# to link against the library, not rebuild it.
build_ca65/
build_llvm/

# Each suite's scratch SD card. The build scripts empty it before a run,
# and the tests write everything they read.
test_ca65/fsroot/*
!test_ca65/fsroot/.gitkeep
test_llvm/fsroot/*
!test_llvm/fsroot/.gitkeep

# Third-party, not committed. See README.md for where to get them.
# ca65/ is an optional repo-local cc65 install that build_ca65.ps1
# prefers when present.
emulator/
llvm-mos/
ca65/
doc/*.pdf
doc/*.md
